@DocFlow.DocumentService.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5007

### Example: Get all documents
GET {{DocFlow.DocumentService.Api_HostAddress}}/documents
Accept: application/json

###

### Example: Upload a document (adjust as needed)
POST {{DocFlow.DocumentService.Api_HostAddress}}/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "example.pdf",
  "content": "base64-encoded-content"
}

###